text:
Gara odeeffannoo Covid-19 bagga naga dhuftan
wa'ee dhibee Covid-19 odeeffannoo fi qajeelcha haaraawaa argaadha
wa'e vaayiraasi korona mal barachuu barbaadtan?
lakkoofsotta yokkin mallatota fayyadamun odeeffannoo haaraawaa argaadha:
1  lakkoofsotta ammayyawa
2 offi kesssan dhibbe irra ittisuuf
3 gaffi kessanif deebii argaadha
4 odeeffannowan sosoba
5 gorsa imaltotaaf
6 odeeffannowani fi ibsaa halla yeroo irra kennamu argachuuf 
7 lammilee birraf ergaa
hoji too'annaa Covid-19 itoophiyaa hordoffuf geessituu kana tuqaa <http://covid19.et/|http://covid19.et/>
